{
  "texts": [
    "Topic 6 documents are focused on studies that applied TM techniques to analyse public health cases.",
    "For example, studies mined topics from user-generated content (UGC) on Covid-19 pandemic (Lande et al. 2023), Covid-19 vaccines (Sv et al. 2021; Ma et al. 2021), Dementia (Abela et al. 2023), Alzheimer's (Tenzek et al. 2023), post-traumatic stress disorder (Grant et al. 2017) and other global public health-related disease treatment.",
    "The findings of Robledo and Zuluaga (2022) revealed that prior studies mined social media data to understand discussions around COVID-19.",
    "Furthermore, we observed some studies mined comments of Reddit users who declared to have mental health issues to understand their discussions.",
    "Laureate et al. (2023) showed that there is a heavy use of TM for social media analysis and is highly valued in the public health domain."
  ]
}